## 9. Replaceability Requirements

The operator must maintain the following artifacts at all times, sufficient for an incoming operator to resume all program functions within 60 days:

- Complete participant registry with current status and history
- All evaluation records and decision rationales
- Current funding disbursement records
- Active program communications and correspondence
- Dependency map and centrality scores (current version)
- Operational runbooks for all recurring program activities

These artifacts are program property, not operator property. They must be transferred intact upon operator change.

